Skills.Name: Red Spear Assault
Skills.Description: Inflicts 5x <code=400,param=201><color=#3398f1>Bleed</color> (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) on all enemies within 100 cm of single target enemy with lowest DEF for 20s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Bleed on all enemies within range

Skills.Name: Scythe of Darkness
Skills.Description:
Inflicts 3-hit DMG on single enemy (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color>).
Further inflicts 5x <code=400,param=201><color=#3398f1>Bleed</color> (<color=red>{3}%</color> of skill user's ATK) for 20s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 3-hit DMG and Bleed on single enemy

Skills.Name: Taste of Calamity
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>{0}%</color> DMG on all enemies. Also inflicts <color=red>{1}%</color> DMG on each enemy multiplied by its total <code=400,param=201><color=#3398f1>Bleed</color> effect(s). Cancels all <color=#3398f1>Bleed</color> effects afterwards. Further lowers Healing Boost by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 7s if Green Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts DMG on all enemies. Further inflicts DMG based on its total Bleed effect(s), cancels Bleed effect(s) afterwards, lowers Healing Boost if Green Elemental

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>75.00%-1500.00%</color> DMG according to Combo Bonus.
